{"article_id":"h0PBd83VqGiYpYBb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Former Virginia Gov . Robert McDonnell , once a rising star in the Republican Party","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"who was considered potential presidential material ,","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"was indicted along with his wife on Tuesday on federal charges","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"of accepting illegal gifts .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"The 14-count indictment ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"culminating a lengthy investigation of their relationship with a Virginia business executive ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"alleges fraud by a public official , false statements , and obstruction .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Gifts","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"valued at a minimum of $ 140,000 in total","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"included designer clothes , a Rolex watch , golf clubs , iPhones and a painting ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"according to a list of items","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"included in the indictment .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"McDonnell ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"who in a statement denied any illegal conduct","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and called the charges federal government overreach ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"was elected in 2009","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"and left office earlier this month","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"after serving one term .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Virginia governors can not serve consecutive terms .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"`` I come before you this evening as someone","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"who has been falsely and wrongfully accused","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"and whose public service has been wrongfully attacked , ''","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"he said in a televised statement .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"The federal probe involved the relationship between the governor and his wife , Maureen , with Jonnie Williams , the chief executive of a troubled nutritional supplement company , Star Scientific .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Authorities allege","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"that Williams gave gifts and loans to the first family of Virginia ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and that they promoted his company .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"McDonnell admitted to poor judgment in an earlier written statement .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"`` I deeply regret accepting legal gifts and loans from Mr. Williams ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"all of which have been repaid with interest ,","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"and I have apologized for my poor judgment","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"for which I take full responsibility , ''","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"`` However , I repeat emphatically","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"that I did nothing illegal for Mr. Williams in exchange for what I believed","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"was his personal generosity and friendship , ''","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"he added .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"McDonnell 's Democratic successor , Terry McAuliffe , issued his own statement","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"after the charges were filed .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"`` As this case progresses ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"it is my sincerest hope","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that justice will be served","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"and that Virginians get the answers","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"to which they are entitled , ''","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"`` As Governor , I will remain focused on leading this Commonwealth in a way","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"that restores Virginians ' trust in government","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"and honors their expectation of transparency and accountability . ''","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Within hours of the indictment , McDonnell 's legal team launched a forceful attack on the government 's case .","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"The lawyers made two legal filings in federal court in Richmond ,","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"one of which invoked an ancient ruler","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"whose tyrannical reign was reputedly marked by financial greed and misdeeds .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"`` It has been a long time","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"since the Roman Emperor Caligula imprisoned people","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"for violating laws","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"written in tiny lettering on a pillar too high","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"to see , ''","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"the lawyers wrote","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"in making a comparison to the federal government 's case against McDonnell .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"McDonnell 's lawyers argued his innocence","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"the charges were built on a `` rickety legal foundation . ''","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"`` To bring today 's indictment ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"the federal government has concocted a never-before-used legal theory","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"manufactured for the sole purpose","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"of prosecuting Governor McDonnell and his wife , ''","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"McDonnell 's lawyers wrote .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"`` This new theory contravenes settled judicial precedent","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"and disregards longstanding Virginia law and practice ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"seeking to punish the McDonnells for conduct","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"that was legal before today , ''","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"the lawyers said .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"The McDonnell legal filings said","depth":4},{"id":74,"text":"Williams is under federal investigation for some of the health claims","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"his company made for its products .","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"But the government has offered `` blanket immunity '' in exchange for cooperation in the McDonnell investigation .","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"Appearing on CNN 's `` Crossfire , ''","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"former Virginia Attorney General Ken Cuccinelli said","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"the indictment was not a surprise","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"considering the public attention","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"the investigation received .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"He believes","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"the charges will `` cause challenges '' for Virginia .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"`` We like to think of ourselves as a pretty smooth-running , clean state .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"Does n't mean everything goes the way","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"we want it to all the time -","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"this puts a dent in that","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"and that 's not something","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"we 're happy to see with the history","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"we 've got ,","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"which has been pretty darn good , ''","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"Cuccinelli , a Republican","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"who served under McConnell ,","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"lost the governor 's election in November to McAuliffe .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":191,"left":0,"right":190,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":190,"left":167,"right":189,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":132,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":114,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":107,"right":113,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":102,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":99,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":97,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":97,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","n